snippet.title: BTS shares how they feel as first time Grammy nominees and performers (FULL) | Entertain This
snippet.description:
Ahead of the 2021 Grammy's, BTS sits down with USA TODAY's Fatima Farha to reveal how they are feeling as first time nominees and performers, what BTS Army can look forward to during their performance, and what "Dynamite" means to them now. Watch the full interview here.

» Subscribe to USA TODAY Entertainment: https://bit.ly/2STkDAa
tags: bts talks about the success of dynamite
